  "detailed_description": "Critical Fishing is a fishing game without a fishing rod. Instead you get a submarine, upgradeable guns and one very angry worm! Start out as a noob with a pistol and become a ricocheting, sawblade throwing, precision shooting, demon summoning, black hole creating, missile launching menace of a worm!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2827930/extras/59904bb7c387ebabe6b35eec422da38c.poster.avif?t=1740251732\" width=560 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2827930/extras/59904bb7c387ebabe6b35eec422da38c.webm?t=1740251732\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2827930/extras/59904bb7c387ebabe6b35eec422da38c.mp4?t=1740251732\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >1. The Dive</h2> <ul class=\"bb_ul\">    <li>Use your remote controlled submarine to collect fish and resources<br>    </li><li>pick up powerful buffs for your next shootout, find permanent upgrades and different treasure chest<br>    </li><li>avoid underwater threats: if you run out of battery everything you have collected during this dive is lost<br>    </li><li>the things you find in this underwater world are radomized each dive</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2827930/extras/8e1b4d210456f1e8279a7a32bc0927d9.poster.avif?t=1740251732\" width=560 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2827930/extras/8e1b4d210456f1e8279a7a32bc0927d9.webm?t=1740251732\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2827930/extras/8e1b4d210456f1e8279a7a32bc0927d9.mp4?t=1740251732\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >2. The Shootout</h2> <ul class=\"bb_ul\">    <li>fling your caught fish into the sky and turn them into many smaller, weird-looking fish for resources and coins<br>    </li><li>choose between 8 upgradeable weapons each with unique special effects<br>    </li><li>equip mods to to personalize your playstyle<br>    </li><li>combine effects for chain reactions and crazy combos<br>    </li><li>use XP to level up and perfect your \"fishing\" skills</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2827930/extras/25d65a0cf627d933485b2f3153ba7031.poster.avif?t=1740251732\" width=560 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2827930/extras/25d65a0cf627d933485b2f3153ba7031.webm?t=1740251732\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2827930/extras/25d65a0cf627d933485b2f3153ba7031.mp4?t=1740251732\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Just ask yourself: is there such a thing as too many homing rockets?",
